            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1251857</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">丰田 Toyota 展示了他们在非汽车领域上的研究，最新研发的健康座椅声称可以只透过坐著就能锻炼。这张摇摇晃晃的座椅能让坐著的人在无意间保持持续的运动，目的是唤醒人类失去了的能力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251867 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251872 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_6e-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_6e-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_6e.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://toyotatimes.jp/en/series/beyondmobility/018.html">Toyota Times</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">这张座椅下有三个支撑柱，其中一个比其他支撑柱短，所以坐著时会有微微的倾斜。三个支撑柱会旋转，不断改变座椅 360 度的倾斜方向。支撑柱的旋转缓慢，需要超过 1 分钟，坐著的人几乎不会留意到倾斜。座椅的原理是出于人类与生俱来的「姿势反射」，会在倾斜中下意识维持身体的姿势，所以坐在座椅上时会自然移动骨盆，而头部保持不动。即使坐著，肌肉也会反复紧张和放松，有助于减轻长途开车时的腰酸背痛。座椅的效果类似于训练核心的平衡球，不同的是它能够自动 360 度旋转。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_20113"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tTnZWctxc44?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251870 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_4_-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_4_-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_4_-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://toyotatimes.jp/en/series/beyondmobility/018.html">Toyota Times</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Toyota 表示你会在坐这个座椅大约 20 分钟后感到疲倦，代表你正在使用不常用的肌肉。前沿研究中心量子人类研究小组专案经理 Tadashi Odashima 提到以前的日本人可携带 100 kg 的米包，反映的不是以前的人有多厉害，而是现代人的退步。这张座椅有望促进肌肉协调，唤醒以前失去了的能力，加强那些不能像肌肉或大脑那样有意识地训练的领域。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://toyotatimes.jp/en/series/beyondmobility/018.html">Toyota Times</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/toyota-bz3c%e3%80%81bz4x-ev-suv-china/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">丰田 bz3c、bz3x 电动 SUV   北京车展现身主攻年轻市场</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/toyota-new-chair-enhancement-by-recovering-inherent-abilities/fun-tech/">丰田 Toyota 研发新型健康座椅　仅靠坐著就能做运动改善腰酸背痛</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
