            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1248810</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>随著现代生活中对高速网络的需求日益增加，家中的网络设备承受著前所未有的压力。无论是在家办公时需要高清视像会议、享受 4K/8K 串流媒体播放 HDR 影片、享受 Hi-Res 音乐，或是玩网上游戏、使用 AR/VR 装置等，对网络频宽和稳定性的要求也愈来愈高。如果你需要更快更稳定的网络连接设备，就要考虑购置 Wi-Fi 7 装置。今次我们会实测 NETGEAR 近日推出的 Nighthawk 系列最新产品：RS300 Wi-Fi 7 路由器。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249316" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00566-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00566-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00566.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Nighthawk RS300 是 NETGEAR 最新推出的 Wi-Fi 7 路由器，速度比 Wi-Fi 6 快 2.4 倍。Nighthawk RS300 最高支援 100 个装置连接，适合需要使用多装置的重度网络使用者。</p><h2>机身设计简约　六角设计</h2><p>今次评测的 NETGEAR Nighthawk RS 300 路由器外观设计线条简约，机身采用六角形设计，放在家中不显突兀，。今代外壳采用不反光磨沙面塑胶，简单不失典雅之余亦有效防止外壳留下指纹，兼顾美观及实用。<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249318" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00022-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00022-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00022.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249347" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00028-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00028-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00028.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249364" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00041-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00041-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00041.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/netgear-orbi-970-2/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】NETGEAR Orbi 970　旗舰级 Wi-Fi 7 + 覆盖范围可达一万呎</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/netgear-july/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 七月优惠推介    Nighthawk WiFi 7 路由器 RS300 全新登场</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/netgear-event-2024june/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 快闪优惠　买指定商品可半价换购智能相架</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>机身多个连接口　方便用家按需求连接</h2><p>路由器具备 1 个 2.5 Gbps 网路埠和 2 个 2.5Gbps 以太网 LAN 埠，另设 2 个 1000Mbps 以太网 LAN 埠，方便用户接驳游戏机、电脑、IoT 装置等高速上网。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00042-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00042-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00042.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲主机设有 1 个 2.5 Gbps 网路埠，和 2 个 2.5Gbps 以太网 LAN 埠</p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/kan00005-694x462.avif 694w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/kan00005.avif 1280w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></picture></p><h2></h2><h2>安装简易　一 App 完成</h2><p>Nighthawk RS300 的安装非常简单，。为顾及新手，Netgear 推出了 Nighthawk 专用应用程式，用户只需连接电源和 LAN 线后下载 Nighthawk 专用 App，扫描路由器的 QR Code，，其后的手续就可交由应用程式自动设置。用户还可以通过 App 进行网络管理，包括暂停互联网、进行网速测试、追踪网络数据使用量，设置单独的访客网络等，让网络管理变得轻松便捷。</p><picture><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249363" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00025-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00025-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00025.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲随附的配件</p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987-268x580.avif 268w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987.avif 416w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228794 sp-no-webp" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987-268x580.jpeg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987.jpeg 416w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲下载「NETGEAR Nighthawk」应用程式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1179926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1.png 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲注册「NETGEAR」帐户</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1179926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1.png 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲注册「NETGEAR」帐户</p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279871-268x580.avif 268w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279871.avif 416w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249278" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择你的产品，小编手上的是 Nighthawk Wi-Fi 路由器</p><picture><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249279" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-1.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲扫描路由器的 QR Code</p><picture><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249361" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00034-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00034-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00034.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲路由器的 QR Code</p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991-268x580.avif 268w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991.avif 416w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></picture><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991-268x580.avif 268w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991.avif 416w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249280" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-2.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲Netgear Nighthawk 应用程式会自动替你完成剩下的步骤，此时需要按「加入」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249289" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-7-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-7-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-7.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p>等手机连接到路由器便可直接上网了。用户事后如果想调整任何设定，亦可利用 Nighthawk 手机 App 遥距管理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249293" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-8-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-8-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-8.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲看见这个页面就代表已经完成扫描所有衞星子机</p><h2>网速测试</h2><p>NETGEAR Nighthakw RS300 是 Wi-Fi 7 装置，能够连接更多装置，覆盖范围和网络表现更佳。我们在办公室进行实际测试，尝试在复杂环境下如何解决无线网络讯号问题。</p><p>首先我们在支援 Wi-Fi 7 的手提电脑使用「Speedtest」网络测速软件，距离路由器 1 米范围内测得下载 2,344 Mbps，上载 2,130 Mbps，延迟 3 ms。</p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsappimage2024052-291x580.avif 291w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsappimage2024052.avif 452w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 291px" /></picture><picture><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251839" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-443x580.jpeg" alt="" width="443" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-443x580.jpeg 443w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072.jpeg 636w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 443px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲离路由器 1 米内（没有墙壁阻隔）</p><p>小编在没有墙壁阻隔的情况下，距离路由器约 5 米再使用测速软件，测得下载 2,007 Mbps，上载 1,457 Mbps，延迟仍能够保持在 4 ms。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251843" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-4-433x580.jpeg" alt="" width="433" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-4-433x580.jpeg 433w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-4.jpeg 617w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 433px" />▲离路由器 5 米的测试结果（没有墙壁阻隔）</p><p>小编这次在隔住一面墙，远离路由器 10 米的情况下使用测速软件，下载录得 1,238 Mbps，上载 918 Mbps，延迟 4 ms，即使隔住一面墙，表现仍然令人满意。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251844" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-5-441x580.jpeg" alt="" width="441" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-5-441x580.jpeg 441w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-5.jpeg 627w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 441px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲离路由器 10 米的测试结果（中间有一面墙）</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/netgear-orbi-970-2/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】NETGEAR Orbi 970　旗舰级 Wi-Fi 7 + 覆盖范围可达一万呎</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/netgear-july/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 七月优惠推介    Nighthawk WiFi 7 路由器 RS300 全新登场</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/netgear-event-2024june/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 快闪优惠　买指定商品可半价换购智能相架</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>总结：平玩 Wi-Fi 7</h2><p>NETGEAR Nighthawk RS300 路由器以其 Wi-Fi 7 技术、高达 9.3Gbps 的速度、广泛的覆盖范围和强大的安全防护，提供了稳定且高效的网络连接。其设计简约，且安装简便，适合家庭和小型办公室使用。Nighthawk RS300 提供高性能、稳定且安全的网络连接，可供需要此类功能的用户考虑。如果你的装置支援 Wi-Fi 7，使用 Nighthakw RS300 后就可以享受高速连线。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/netgear-orbi-970-2/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】NETGEAR Orbi 970　旗舰级 Wi-Fi 7 + 覆盖范围可达一万呎</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/netgear-july/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 七月优惠推介    Nighthawk WiFi 7 路由器 RS300 全新登场</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/netgear-event-2024june/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 快闪优惠　买指定商品可半价换购智能相架</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/netgear-nighthawk-rs300/wireless-home/routers/">【评测】NETGEAR Nighthawk RS300　平玩 Wi-Fi7 + 设单独访客网络</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
